text: Apple A5 is a chip that was made by Apple. It has 2 cores and runs at 1.0 GHz (for iPad 2 and iPad mini (1st generation)) or 800 MHz (for iPhone 4S and iPod Touch (5th generation)). It is first released in 2011. Category:32-bit Apple A series Category:Dual-core processors Category:Apple silicon released in 2010s
title: Apple A5
